{"tid":1473758,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷獲准保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:55:02.000Z","uid":53003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71c13bbbd31eea033f6c87a0363ecb5f79c4d3e8","tid":1473758,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"佔中發起人戴耀廷4月被裁定串謀犯公眾妨擾，以及煽惑他人犯公眾妨擾罪成，判囚16個月，上訴庭今日處理他的保釋等候上訴申請。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭副庭長麥機智批准戴耀廷，以現金10萬元保釋，並要交出旅遊證件，期間若需離港，需要經由法庭批准，要亦居住於向法庭申報的住址。<br />\n<br />\n而有關戴耀廷等被告上訴的案件，排期於明年2月24日至26日聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474799-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474799-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg3jL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=d3d5a85d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474799-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=92f8e493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474799-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bad68ad2d4ef0556163eea0a89d8566facfaedc6","tid":1473758,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}